    <item>
      <title>中国银行2021年以来首次上调房贷利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/china-banks-raise-mortgage-rates-for-the-first-time-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家研究公司的最新数据显示，由于房地产市场持续低迷和世界第二大经济体增长放缓导致利润率收窄，中国的各银行三年来首次提高了新抵押贷款成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/china-banks-raise-mortgage-rates-for-the-first-time-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:17:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Eneos 考虑首次公开募股 (IPO) 高达 70% 的 JX Advanced Metals 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/eneos-is-said-to-mull-ipo-of-up-to-70-of-chip-material-maker-jx</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本炼油商 Eneos Holdings Inc. 正考虑在首次股票出售中出售高达 70% 的 JX Advanced Metals Corp. 股份，募资额可能高达 7000 亿日元（45 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/eneos-is-said-to-mull-ipo-of-up-to-70-of-chip-material-maker-jx</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CATL 考虑在香港第二次上市，筹资至少 50 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/catl-is-said-to-consider-hk-listing-to-raise-at-least-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，宁德时代科技股份有限公司正考虑在香港进行第二次上市，可能募集至少 50 亿美元资金，这将是自 2021 年初以来香港规模最大的一次上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/catl-is-said-to-consider-hk-listing-to-raise-at-least-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨后，中国人民银行提供自 7 月以来最强人民币支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/pboc-s-daily-yuan-fix-support-grows-to-level-last-seen-in-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国联邦储备委员会对未来降息发出警告后，中国通过每日参考汇率加大了对人民币的支持，这提振了美元，并导致离岸人民币跌至一年新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/pboc-s-daily-yuan-fix-support-grows-to-level-last-seen-in-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 01:21:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鹰派降息刺激市场，亚洲货币暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-tumble-as-fed-s-hawkish-cut-jolts-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三新兴市场货币的下跌延续至亚洲交易时段，韩元跌至金融危机以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-tumble-as-fed-s-hawkish-cut-jolts-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 01:12:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储刺激比特币价格遭遇 9 月以来最大跌幅，比特币测试 10 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bitcoin-btc-tests-100-000-after-fed-spurs-worst-drop-since-september</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储暗示对未来降息空间更加谨慎后，比特币跌至 100,000 美元以下，这是投机性投资普遍回落的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bitcoin-btc-tests-100-000-after-fed-spurs-worst-drop-since-september</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 00:11:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师称日本央行可能犹豫加息 日元面临下跌风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-markets-may-see-outsized-slump-after-fed-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，由于看到美联储降息后美国股市暴跌，日本央行可能不愿在其政策会议上发表过于鹰派的言论，日元面临进一步下跌的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-markets-may-see-outsized-slump-after-fed-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 00:04:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
